Where to Watch

A young boy accidentally triggers the return of Predators to Earth, only now they are even stronger and more lethal after genetically upgrading themselves with DNA from other species in the universe. It's up to a ragtag group of ex-soldiers to stop them, along with unexpected help from a disgruntled science teacher.
